### DO NOT
- Modify any other file
- Add the feature to `default` features — it must be opt-in
- Add any new crate dependencies
- Change existing dependency declarations
- Modify `lib.rs` or any `.rs` file — this batch only touches `Cargo.toml`

### Existing Code Context

`crates/roko-cli/Cargo.toml` (relevant sections):
```toml
